comments: Embiid (PHI) extends his chest slightly into Antetokounmpo (MIL) as they come together in the post, and marginal body contact occurs.
Niang (PHI) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently exiting.
Niang (PHI) and Wigginton (MIL) make incidental foot-to-foot contact before Niang absorbs the oncoming contact to his body during the screen.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) jumps from point A to point B and makes contact with Maxey's (PHI) lower body that affects his driving shot attempt.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: Middleton (MIL) passes the ball out-of-bounds.
Ibaka's (MIL) arm is not in a legal guarding position when he makes contact with Embiid (PHI) that affects his upward shooting motion on the jump shot attempt.
Embiid (PHI) is in the paint for less than three seconds when the shot is imminent.
Maxey (PHI) makes contact with Holiday's (MIL) left arm during his upward shooting motion that affects his driving shot attempt.
Holiday (MIL) attempts to go for the steal and makes illegal contact with the right arm of Embiid (PHI).

Replay review of the loose ball foul called on Antetokounmpo (MIL) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed successful. Korkmaz (PHI) and Antetokounmpo both gain possession of the rebound, which results in a tie-up.
Maxey (PHI) and Holiday (MIL) briefly tangle arms and engage and disengage during the rebound.
Niang (PHI) makes contact to Holiday's (MIL) right arm that affects his ability to pass the ball.
Portis (MIL) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Korkmaz (PHI) and firms up to absorb the oncoming contact to his body.
Middleton (MIL) commits a take foul on Niang (PHI).
Harris (PHI) is trailing Middleton (MIL) when the marginal contact occurs during the screen with Ibaka (MIL).  Ibaka loses his footing and is not dislodged from his position by Harris.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) makes contact with Maxey's (PHI) right arm during the rebound that impedes his ability to secure the ball.
Embiid (PHI) makes marginal contact with Antetokounmpo's (MIL) right arm during his shooting motion that does not affect his driving shot attempt.

Before the ball is in play, Maxey (PHI) tosses the ball to Embiid (PHI) so he can inbound the basketball.  The ball goes off of Embiid and Antetokounmpo (MIL) picks it up and attempts a shot.  The play is blown dead and the basket is not scored since the ball was never in play.

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: The ball makes contact with Nwora's (MIL) right leg when it is positioned out of bounds and possession should remain with the 76ers.
Embiid (PHI) commits a take foul on Antetokounmpo (MIL) prior to him beginning his upward shooting motion.
Thybulle (PHI) legally contests Middleton's (MIL) jump shot attempt.  Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
